  "3009410": {
    "name": "Moor Rail",
    "steam_appid": 3009410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/3371815ca793b8a7f4ff26a2bc4d2325.avif?t=1770377361\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras_big/3371815ca793b8a7f4ff26a2bc4d2325.avif?t=1770377361 width=800 height=282 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>《穆尔铁路》是一款以柴油朋克为背景的战略横向卷轴射击动作游戏。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以强化列车，增加载重量或提升速度，也可以安装辅助或攻击的车辆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还可以雇佣多名在列车上并肩作战并协助战斗的佣兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接到委托并运输物品的运输公司快递员万寿菊，接到了一个可疑的委托。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >任务是在远方的村庄代购一个叫做“核心”的物品，并运送到目的地，虽然只是一个简单的委托，但报酬却是可疑的巨额金钱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然有些怀疑，但因为是委托，她还是开始了运输。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她能平安地完成运送吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/e1311a76c2a0459ed80c8b888c80d47a.poster.avif?t=1770377361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/e1311a76c2a0459ed80c8b888c80d47a.webm?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/e1311a76c2a0459ed80c8b888c80d47a.mp4?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆在奔跑的列车上击退袭来的敌人，抵达目的地。</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/cdf447a1ae67167f8e6b7d4f0a837fdc.poster.avif?t=1770377361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/cdf447a1ae67167f8e6b7d4f0a837fdc.webm?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/cdf447a1ae67167f8e6b7d4f0a837fdc.mp4?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以使用每个角色专属的技能和武器来击退敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用技能和道具使玩家获得有利条件，带领胜利。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆小心强大且难以击败的变异Boss和掠夺者。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/afc1d7a7a3739d9a2baabed7b8b3b374.poster.avif?t=1770377361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/afc1d7a7a3739d9a2baabed7b8b3b374.webm?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/afc1d7a7a3739d9a2baabed7b8b3b374.mp4?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >会出现什么样的Boss呢？那个Boss会使用什么样的模式呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss战中必须掌握其模式才能生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败Boss后能获得怎样的巨大奖励呢？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆为了到达目的地，请在车站进行整备。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/de02aeb2ce7d2a064bfcc2b613651ac0.poster.avif?t=1770377361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/de02aeb2ce7d2a064bfcc2b613651ac0.webm?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/de02aeb2ce7d2a064bfcc2b613651ac0.mp4?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以根据列车的作用进行布置，展开多样的战略，通过升级运营性能更好的列车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，还可以升级在游戏中发挥有利效果的被动技能和玩家角色，使游戏更加顺利。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆为了进入下一个章节，请完成任务。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/c2c8f5e3e4e2a9f72d7f6e042b33e84f.poster.avif?t=1770377361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/c2c8f5e3e4e2a9f72d7f6e042b33e84f.webm?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/c2c8f5e3e4e2a9f72d7f6e042b33e84f.mp4?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请选择并进行玩家想要的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果放弃或失败任务，将被征收巨额罚款。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >失败是罚款，成功是奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/2964be536f9e758224bbca888c8e6886.poster.avif?t=1770377361\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/2964be536f9e758224bbca888c8e6886.webm?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3009410/extras/2964be536f9e758224bbca888c8e6886.mp4?t=1770377361\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
